x.  Requirements

    -   Microsoft .NET Framework 3.5 or later, or Mono 2.0 or later
    -   A Unix shell and standard command-line tools
    -   GNU Make, at least 3.80 but preferably newer
    -   Makery build system, available from SVN at
        http://makery.sourceforge.net/


